6 An Act relating to civil procedure; amending Section
1439, Chapter 321, O.S.L. 2022 (12 O.S. Supp. 2024,
7 Section 1439), which relates to the Oklahoma Citizens
Participation Act; excluding certain legal action
8 from act; and providing an effective date.
